Mana conservation is capped at exactly 25%.  Meaning a spell even after conservation and scm will take 75%.  In the example of Divine Light, which I have tested.  SCM 3 (which gives a savings of 22% if specialized alteration from 350) costed 273 roughly every time.<br>
<br>
