<br>
However, with Judgement, I noticed a big surprise.<br>
<br>
Without the ODS, Judgement only costed 286 mana (12% mana saving from 325) I was able to cast this 13 times.<br>
<br>
With the ODS, Judgement costed 254 mana( 22% mana savings from 325) and I was able to cast this 15 times.  <br>
<br>
Minor mana regen made the difference.  But it <br>
