<br>
Someone with SCM2 with an item with AE3 will get the most of out their specialization type spells.  <br>
<br>
Therefore a druid with SCM3 specialized in Conjuration will notice minimal difference with a AE3 item, as the difference is only 3%.<br>
<br>
However if that druid specialized in Conuration and is casting Breath of Ro, a Evocation DoT, you should notice a difference in the number of times you can cast the spell with a MC3 item on.<br>
<br>
Vice versa for those specialized in Evoc.  <br>
<br>
