<br>
If you already have MC3 focus and SCM2 with max specs, you are saving 10 + 5 + 3 = 18% for 50 specs, and 10 + 5 + 11 = 26% (but capped supposedly at 25%).  Getting SCM3 in this case then gets you an additional 5% on your 50-specced spells, and nothing on your main specced spells.<br>
<br>
